{"tid":542101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 數萬人重返金鐘","createTime":"2018-01-27T06:58:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T13:56:52.000Z","uid":28366,"like":187,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"92fb8a0a43efa1ed60afa75df551cb58e5466f5a","tid":542101,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T06:58:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/27/145618_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F27%2F145618_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=ca094f30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">金鐘的示威者紛紛舉起發光的手機屏幕，一同展示爭取真普選的決心。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/27/145632_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F27%2F145632_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=752dfba2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">入夜後，在中環聚集的示威者漸多，佔據大部份路面。</span><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】 佔領行動遍地開花，作為第一個佔領點的金鐘，是警方鎮壓最暴力的地方，但鎮壓越大，出來聲援的市民就越多。前晚入夜後，數以千計市民紛紛躺在車行的干諾道中上歇息，不願離去。有人慨嘆，在中環上班數年，從未如此仔細觀察過中環、感受香港。昨晚再有數萬名市民齊聚金鐘，並向中環推進。由灣仔紅十字會坐到中環畢打街，萬千燈光照亮半個港島。"},{"pid":"365fa8f61d72b566cbd15c110e388194c53b89bd","tid":542101,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T07:00:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c884a628f7debfaa0f31ec807c2292059a0cdf3d","tid":542101,"uid":4917,"like":74,"dislike":3,"score":71,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T07:00:52.000Z","msg":"示弱者"},{"pid":"98fd9c768b27225d214d2d58adf2e40138aedbea","tid":542101,"uid":62842,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T07:01:21.000Z","msg":"一去不復返"},{"pid":"2b82cd3da8650a84734b19f9896a467dfac86286","tid":542101,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-27T07